---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 space-y-5 text-gray-300">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Terms of Service</h1>

    <p>
      Welcome to our Minecraft web services. Please read these terms carefully before using our services.
    </p>

    <p>
      By accessing or using our services (such as purchasing in-game items, accessing content, or joining servers),
      you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must not use our services.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">1. Use of Service</h2>
    <p>
      Our services are intended for Minecraft players who wish to purchase cosmetic items, access additional content,
      or view information related to our Minecraft server or shop.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">2. User Conduct</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-4">
      <li>Do not exploit bugs or use unauthorized mods.</li>
      <li>No spamming, harassment, or toxic behavior on any of our platforms.</li>
      <li>Respect other players and follow server rules at all times.</li>
    </ul>

