    <p>
      All payments are final and non-refundable. Please ensure you are logged into the correct Minecraft account
      before making any purchase.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">4. Account Suspension</h2>
    <p>
      We reserve the right to suspend or ban any account that violates these terms, with or without notice.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p>
      We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Continued use of our services means you accept the changes.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-6">
      Last updated: August 7, 2025
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
